@theopolis Thanks for your comments. I was modeling these configuration properties after:
https://github.com/edenhill/librdkafka/blob/master/CONFIGURATION.md

Some one opened a issue about supporting SASL and other options. Possible values supported by librdkafka are: plaintext, ssl, sasl_plaintext, sasl_ssl. Until SASL support is built into librdkafka formula we won't be able to add these extra options. Hence I left this as string instead of boolean.

